{"lemma":"ثَمَّةَ","slug":"ثَمَّةَ","root":"ث.م.م","root_slug":"ث-م-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ث-م-م","pos":"ADV","pos_camel":"adv","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adv"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n4663","n4667","n4668"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AB%D9%8E%D9%85%D9%8E%D9%91%D8%A9%D9%8E"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adv","gloss":"there"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n4663","headword_ar":"ثَمَّهُ","root":"vm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, * K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vam~N","text_ar":"ثَمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repaired it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put it into a good, sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"right, state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K;) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by filling up its interstices, &c.,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S.) Hence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamamotu A^umuwriY","text_ar":"ثَمَمْتُ اُمُورِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I put my affairs into a good, sound, right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proper, state; restored them to such a state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"set them right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) And hence also the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kun~aA A^ahola vam~ihi waram~ihi","text_ar":"كُنَّا اَهْلَ ثَمِّهِ وَرَمِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We were the fit persons to put it into a good, sound, right,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"proper, state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]; (S;) occurring in a trad.; accord. to the relaters thereof,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"warum~ihi","text_ar":"وَرُمِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~ihi","text_ar":"ثُمِّهِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but A 'Obeyd holds the former reading to be the right. (T.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spread"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a skin of milk,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and put it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vmAm","text_ar":"ثمام"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"above it, in order that the sun might not strike it, and its milk become consequently decomposed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"curdled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b3-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He stuffed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"either with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"or absolutely: for]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a","text_ar":"ثُمَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it was stuffed."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He collected it together;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K;) namely, a thing; (S, M;) mostly used in relation to dry herbage. (M, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~a lahaA","text_ar":"ثُمَّ لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Collect thou"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, the cattle &c.; like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vimo lahaA","text_ar":"ثِمْ لَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wavama","text_ar":"وَثَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yavum~uhu wayaqum~uhu","text_ar":"هُوَ يَثُمُّهُ وَيَقُمُّهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sweeps it, and collects the good and the bad."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vam~a AlT~aEaAma","text_ar":"ثَمَّ الطَّعَامَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) [aor. and] inf. n. as above, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate the good of the food and the bad thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qam~ahu","text_ar":"قَمَّهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vam~atopu","text_ar":"ثَمَّتْةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, * S, M, K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a ewe or a goat, M, K, or, as some say, only the latter, M)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pulled it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plucked it, up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"out, with her mouth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, M, K;) namely, a thing, (T, M,) or a plant, (S, K,) and anything by which she passed. (TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vam~a yadahu biAlHa$iy$i","text_ar":"ثَمَّ يَدَهُ بِالحَشِيشِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlA^aroDi","text_ar":"بِالاَرْضِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M,) [aor. and] inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wiped his hand"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the dry herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","T","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n4667","headword_ar":"ثَمَّةٌ","root":"vm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAmN","text_ar":"ثُمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n4668","headword_ar":"ثُمَّةٌ","root":"vm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A handful of dry herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K.) ―         -b2-  Also n. un. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vum~N","text_ar":"ثُمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAmN","text_ar":"ثُمَامٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see the next paragraph in six places."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}